# WooCommerce Integration

## Webhook Processing
- Azure Functions receive WooCommerce webhook payloads
- Validate webhook signatures before processing
- Store raw payloads for debugging
- Process orders, products, and customer data

## WooCommerce REST API
- Use requests library with API key authentication
- Base URL pattern: https://store-url/wp-json/wc/v3/
- Handle pagination with per_page and page parameters
- Rate limiting: respect WooCommerce API limits
